snippet.title: Bonsai and Gardening Zone
snippet.description:
I am Shireesh Sharma and you are on 'Bonsai and Gardening Zone'. This channel is about living art of bonsai, as well as gardening tricks and techniques.
Bonsai and Gardening zone is a platform for bonsai beginners and enthusiasts to know and learn about starting and maintaining a bonsai easily, from soil mix to bonsai training, wiring, pruning branches and roots, bending, styling, ramification, potting, reporting, new experiments and many more.
Also videos for hobby gardeners and biginners, for growing organic veggies, fruits flowering and decorative plants in balcony or on terrace garden. Making soil mix, organic compost, fertilizers & pesticides.
Professional secreats, tricks, hacks, FAQ and DIY videos in English and Hindi, and a lot more. 
Thanks for visiting. Please subscribe to this channel to watch more.
